text: Karyn White (born 14 October 1965 in Los Angeles) is an American R&B; singer. She was very popular in the late 1980s and early 1990s. Her hit singles include "Secret Rendezvous" and "Superwoman". ==References== Category:African- American singers Category:Singers from California Category:American R&B; singers Category:1965 births Category:Living people
